The,SkyWise,Current,Forecast,API,allows,developers,to,retrieve,current,and,forecast,weather,information,Weather,observations,are,updated,hourly,in,the,U,S,and,every,three,hours,globally,The,day,weather,forecasts,are,updated,every,hours,Forecasts,are,derived,from,a,combination,of,weather,prediction,models,at,the,National,Center,of,Environmental,Prediction,and,internal,models,at,Weather,Decision,Technologies